 your dedicated nurse who can assist you with navigating the healthcare system coordinate many of the resources you have with blue shield provide you with information on care or refer you to a specialty program if you are coping with a complex medical issue are pregnant or if you have musculoskeletal issues for example provide a cd with guided imagery to help pre surgery patients better prepare for surgery and experience faster recovery cds are also available to manage and reduce stress chronic pain depression smoking and help with weight loss find resources to help you or other family members if you or a family member is scheduled for surgery leslie can explain the procedure answer your questions and offer hints and tips on other issues that you might not have considered for example if you re about to have knee replacement surgery will your house be ready for you return are area rugs removed to avoid tripping is there a clear path to the bathroom she is also available to counsel family members on aftercare and if needed provide helpful resources to support the whole family leslie owen epo nurse health advocate 1101 welch road call 650 736 0780 for an appointment appointments available monday friday from 8 am to 4 pm jane fergason ppo nurse health advocate call 866 596 7557 nursehelp for immediate answers to health questions 877 304 0504 24 hours a day 7 days a week home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
